*pfeifer-sources-2.4.21.1_pre4-r1 (06 Jan 2004)

  06 Jan 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> pfeifer-sources-2.4.21.1_pre4-r1.ebuild,
  pfeifer-sources-2.4.21.1_pre4.ebuild,
  files/pfeifer-sources-2.4.21.1_pre4-r1.CAN-2003-0985.patch,
  files/pfeifer-sources-2.4.21.1_pre4-r1.rtc_fix.patch:
  Added patches to address the security vulnerabilities in bugs #37292 and
  #37317. Old revision removed.

  01 Dec 2003; Brian Jackson <iggy@gentoo.org>
  pfeifer-sources-2.4.20.1_pre11.ebuild,
  pfeifer-sources-2.4.20.1_pre12.ebuild, pfeifer-sources-2.4.21.1_pre4.ebuild,
  files/do_brk_fix.patch: Fix do_brk() vulnerability.

  20 Nov 2003; Brandon Low <lostlogic@gentoo.org>
  pfeifer-sources-2.4.20.1_pre11.ebuild,
  pfeifer-sources-2.4.20.1_pre12.ebuild, pfeifer-sources-2.4.21.1_pre4.ebuild:
  Move version handling logic to after inherit kernel, or insert it where
  necessary.

